title: Core Dive v1.2 [PD]
description:
Core Dive is a physics puzzle game in which the player guides a ball through labyrinthine temples situated in various landscapes, ranging from islands floating in the sky to claustrophobic caverns in the core of the planet. 

Play through 100 levels and dive deep into the center of the globe to discover the secrets of Core Dive!

What's New:

-Added Mute Button to title screen
-Added alternate tilt calibration in pause menu
-Fixed problems with the ball getting pinched between platforms
-Fixed some walls not breaking properly
